    <item>
      <title>Intersolar 2016</title>
      <link>http://www.infinitefingers.com/news/intersolar-2016/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://www.infinitefingers.com/news/intersolar-2016/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Infinite Fingers presented the Li-ion battery clustering solution in collaboration with Autarctech, during Intersolar 2016.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The Infinite Fingers BMS Master allows multiple standalone AutarcTech LiConnect batteries to be wired up in parallel and
be treated as a single battery stack. The Infinite Fingers BMS Master controls all the underlying batteries, aggregating
the data and passing it up to the inverter.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For more technical information please &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.autarctech.de/en/bms-balancer/&#34;&gt;visit the AutarcTech website&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Below are a few visual impressions from Intersolar Europe 2016:&lt;/p&gt;

